response.overview: Two sisters each fall in love with the same man, setting off a conflict within their family. As emotions and loyalties are tested, the sisters must confront their feelings, the expectations of their family, and the meaning of love. The story emphasizes the bonds of family, the strength found in faith and prayer, and explores what it takes to let go, make wise decisions, and allow love (and life) to unfold with integrity.
response.title: Not My Man
